      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'showroom condition.' This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and displays a deep, glass-like luster on its original paint, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. There are absolutely no dings, stone chips, or swirl marks to be found across the bodywork. Step inside to find an interior that remains in pristine state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and completely free of creases, while the carpets have been protected by original factory mats since day one. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions with out-of-the-box precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a full, documented service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by authorized technicians. The engine bay is spotless, the transmission shifts with seamless fluidity, and the high-performance tires show virtually no wear. This is a rare, collector-grade example that has been pampered throughout its life, offering the next owner the experience of a brand-new vehicle.",
